reviewText: not as good as the others in this series..sorry to say..:(...
Love this movie.  First saw it in 1974 when I was in the Army.  I purchased it because of the memories.  A little on the adult side, although not so much based on today's standards.
Silly old movie I saw years ago, but fun.

This movie was a staple on Cinemax a good number of years ago.  Lots of nudity from cute young ladies but no real sex scenes.  Lots of funny scenes both with and without nudity.  The film transfer is quite good.  The first in a series of four movies and the best of them.  Well worth seeing.
